  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another fertilizer ship will arrive in a fortnight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, another ship with 21,000 metric tons of urea is scheduled to arrive in Sri Lanka within the next fortnight.",
        "The stock of fertilizer is planned to be given to the farmers at the beginning of the cultivation activities in the high season.",
        "Also, the Ministry of Agriculture says that the World Bank has already agreed to provide 110 million dollars to purchase 1,50,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer for the 2022/2023 season.",
        "Out of the 65,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer given to Sri Lanka under the Indian loan scheme, 44,000 metric tons, which is the first batch, has been packed and distributed in the warehouses of the government-owned Lanka Fertilizer Company and Commercial Fertilizer Company.",
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, 3000 metric tons of urea fertilizer has been distributed to agricultural service centers all over the island within a period of three days.",
        "The second batch of Indian fertilizers is scheduled to arrive in Sri Lanka in another fortnight."
      ],
